    "Title": "Surveillance Termination",
    "Description": "It seems our struggle to free Humanity has got the government lapdogs back on Earth feeling nervous. Recent scans discovered an orbital sentry at ~mission(location|address) that we believe is part of an UEE espionage campaign. Good credits says they\u2019re handing the data direct to the slinks themselves. \n\nOnly one sentry has been detected so far, but who knows how big the operation will grow if it\u2019s not taken off-line. Shouldn\u2019t be too much trouble for a skilled merc. If that sounds like you, payment will be sent promptly once the sentry is destroyed. Plus, XenoThreat will remember that you\u2019re someone willing to fight for what\u2019s right.\n\nComm. Spec. Engler",
